videos.description: Fabian Johnson run for no gain to the Buff 24 Fabian Johnson fumbled, forced by Ishmael Hargrove, recovered by Buff Ryan Williamson
videos.headline: Buffalo recovers after stripping ball from Western Michigan RB

videos.description: Zach Terrell pass complete to Corey Davis for 22-yards for a TD
videos.headline: Corey Davis puts defender through spin cycle, puts Broncos on board

videos.description: Zach Terrell connects with Jarvion Franklin, who gets away from Buffalo defenders for a 20-yard touchdown in the final minutes of the second quarter.
videos.headline: Western Michigan RB shrugs off defender for TD

videos.description: Quint Kessenich interviews WMU HC P.J. Fleck at the half
videos.headline: Halftime interview with Western Michigan coach P.J. Fleck who says Broncos are beating themselves despite halftime lead

videos.headline: Michael Henry takes the screen 65-yards to the house

videos.headline: Fabian Johnson puts finishing touches on Bronco victory

videos.description: Quint Kessenich interviews WMU HC P.J. Fleck after Broncos victory over Bulls
videos.headline: Postgame interview with WMU head coach P.J. Fleck who talks about teams "historic" week culminating in the victory over Buffalo

videos.description: P.J. Fleck and company celebrate their victory in the locker room
videos.headline: WMU head coach P.J. Fleck continues his postgame tradition, runs and jumps into the waiting arms of his team

videos.description: P.J. Fleck delivers fiery postgame speech in locker room
videos.headline: P.J. Fleck discusses his team's journey from eleven losses to eleven wins in rousing postgame speech.

videos.description: No. 21 Western Michigan crosses a lot of things off their holiday wish list Saturday with a win against Buffalo, SportsCenter recaps the big day in Kalamazoo.
